{"tid":2486354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國際安全論壇要頒獎給蔡英文，外媒報導：加拿大政府施壓「敢頒就撤贊助」","createTime":"2021-04-13T00:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T05:49:23.000Z","uid":366655,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"61b62ab224c794e00cd17dca816cf0dc6113f1b2","tid":2486354,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"台灣總統蔡英文將被國際知名的安全論壇頒獎，但外媒報導加拿大政府警告論壇，若頒給蔡英文，會撤回對該論壇的資助。<br />\n<br />\n「哈利法克斯國際安全論壇」（Halifax International Security Forum, HFX）總部設於美國華府，是全球最知名的國防論壇之一，宗旨為「加強民主國家間的戰略合作」。<br />\n<br />\n這次可能頒給總統蔡英文的獎名為「馬侃公共服務領袖獎」（John McCain Prize），該獎於 2018 年創設，當年頒給收留難民的希臘勒斯博島（Lesbos）的居民，2019 年頒給香港抗爭公民，今年則要頒給蔡英文，表揚她堅定對抗中國持續不斷的壓力。此決定也經過馬侃的遺孀辛蒂（Cindy McCain）首肯。<br />\n<br />\n《政客》（Politico）報導，當加拿大政府得知這個頒獎計畫，表示如果「哈利法克斯國際安全論壇」頒獎給蔡英文， 加拿大政府會撤回對論壇的資助。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2021/04/12/hfx-forum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2021%2F04%2F12%2Fhfx-forum%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=319911a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2021/04/12/hfx-forum/</a>"},{"pid":"f08185b57a27e526c1967c7ef023084b4fe4d97b","tid":2486354,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T00:05:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://buzzorange.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=2d4722e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">buzzorange.com</a>"},{"pid":"b973764c8cd34a12aa0d434527c2aea12847816b","tid":2486354,"uid":235853,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"呢個網站係著名假新聞網站嚟咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2ffc7a19a1f75c989bc538a3a984371c0d2164","tid":2486354,"uid":366655,